Usage: ./map_test [-r] [-w] [-s size] [-p string] [-o offset]
-r: perform read -- use -o and -s flags to select offset and size of data to read
-w: perform write -- use -o and -p flags to select offset and string to write

string: string to write in write case
size: size to read in read case
offset: decimal offset from base address of smartDIMM
